Authentication system
--------------------------------------------
 User
   Username (univocal)
   Email    (univocal)
   ...
   Group, ...
   Role, ...

 Group
   Name     (univocal)
   Role, ...

 Role
   Name     (univocal)
   Value    (univocal)
 
 roles list (fixed):
   name          | value
  -------------------------------------------
   administrator | ROLE_ADMINISTRATOR (1)
   operator      | ROLE_OPERATOR      (2)
   customer      | ROLE_CUSTOMER      (4)
   supplier      | ROLE_SUPPLIER      (8)
   guest         | ROLE_GUEST         (1024)
